## Group Block

# /block/{index}

## GET

This retrieves the block specified by the index as Json

+ Parameters

    + index (number) - The block index
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "status": "success",
              "result": 
                {
                  "index": 0,
                  "transactions": [],
                  "nonce": 0,
                  "prev_hash": "genesis",
                  "merkle_tree_root": "",
                  "timestamp": 0,
                  "difficulty": 17,
                  "kind": "SLOW",
                  "address": "genesis"
                }
            }

        
## block/header [GET /block/{index}/header]

This retrieves the block header at the specified index as Json

+ Parameters

    + index (number) - The block index
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "status": "success",
              "result": 
                {
                  "index": 0,
                  "nonce": 0,
                  "prev_hash": "genesis",
                  "merkle_tree_root": "",
                  "timestamp": 0,
                  "difficulty": 17
                }
            }


## block/transactions [GET /block/{index}/transactions{?page}{?per_page}{?direction}]

This retrieves the transactions for the block specified at index as Json

+ Parameters

    + index (number) - The block index
    + page: 0 (number, optional) - The page
    + per_page: 20 (number, optional) - The number of items per page
    + direction: up (string, optional) - The direction (up = ascending, down = descending)
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

